==English==
===Noun===
'''bum''' ('''plural'' '''[[bums]]''')

# (''British, Australian, informal'') The [[buttocks]] or [[anus]].
# (''US'') A [[hobo]]

====Synonyms====
*(''hobo''): [[hobo]], [[homeless]] person, [[tramp]]
*(''buttocks or anus''): [[arse]] (''UK, Irish, Australian''), [[ass]] (''North American''), [[backside]], [[bottom]], [[butt]] (''UK''), [[buttocks]] (''technical''), [[heinie]] (''US''), [[fanny]] (''US''), [[tush]] (''US''), [[tushie]] (''US'')
*(''buttocks specifically'') [[butt cheeks]] (''US''), [[cheek]]s
*(''anus specifically''): [[anus]] (''technical''), [[arsehole]] (''UK, Irish, Australian'')

